OL,3,CLib Dems celebrate taking Portsmouth
OL,4,Cas Labour loses control of Southampton
OL,6,FThe Conservatives lost control of
OL,7,FHampshire County Council for the first
OL,8,Ftime in almost 30 years, leaving the
OL,9,Fcouncil - one of the largest
OL,10,Fauthorities in England - under no
OL,11,Foverall control.
OL,13,FThere was also further pain for Prime
OL,14,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer, whose party
OL,15,Flost control of Southampton City
OL,16,FCouncil, with no one party taking
OL,17,Foverall power.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
