CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778242270
OL,3,CLib Dems celebrate taking Portsmouth
OL,4,Cas Labour loses control of Southampton
OL,6,FLabour, meanwhile, lost all five of
OL,7,Ftheir seats and Reform picked up five.
OL,9,FDiscussing the Portsmouth results, Sir
OL,10,FEd said: "It's a fantastic result here
OL,11,Fin Portsmouth.
OL,13,F"Reform threw everything at it, but we
OL,14,Fwon. We've taken control of this
OL,15,Fcouncil and we've shown across the
OL,16,Fcountry that it's the Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrats that can hold off and beat
OL,18,FReform."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
