OL,3,CLib Dems celebrate taking Portsmouth
OL,4,Cas Labour loses control of Southampton
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe added: "Both the Conservatives and
OL,12,FLabour need to smell the coffee.
OL,14,F"The old parties are out and we are
OL,15,Fthe only party offering the change
OL,16,Fthat Britain needs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
