OL,3,CLib Dems celebrate taking Portsmouth
OL,4,Cas Labour loses control of Southampton
OL,6,F"Yes, there are extreme populist
OL,7,Fparties fuelling on people's desire
OL,8,Ffor change, but those parties
OL,9,Fbasically offer change by burning it
OL,10,Fall down.
OL,12,F"We're the only party of building it
OL,13,Fup."
